<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2020_0203m4a-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Bernie sanders speaks into a microphone surrounded by people holding &quot;Medicare for All&quot; posters" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2020_0203m4a-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2020_0203m4a-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2020_0203m4a-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2020_0203m4a-1200x900.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
