<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-sanders-threatens-the-establishment-by-inspiring-popular-movements/">Noam Chomsky: Sanders Threatens the Establishment by Inspiring Popular Movements</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">While the establishment views Sanders as dangerous, Trump is waging war against life on Earth.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/c-j-polychroniou/" itemprop="url" rel="author">C.J. Polychroniou</a></span>, </dd>
